<br>
Also get your Sol Ro temple focus items if you haven't, you need to buy gems for those.<br>
<br>
Look into a stein of mogguk and Gatorscale sleeves if you need int.  There should also be some glove slot items that give you int.  I'm not sure what the glove selection is like now, I wore Impskin which should be cheap now.  If you have faction you may even be able to buy Thurg or Skyshrine multiquest gloves(&quot;Arch Mage&quot; or &quot;Prestidigitator&quot; gloves).  The hard part of those are the crushed topaz you need to complete the quest.  The stats are good though, and they may be out of your price range I don't know.<br>
<br>
Honestly.. first thing I would do if I were you is go to the bazaar and do a search for all those slots that are empty.  The cheapest and largest upgrades will most likely be to put items in those slots. <p><center><br>
